Yes.

295
00:16:18,380 --> 00:16:20,660
[Qian Residence]

296
00:16:31,000 --> 00:16:31,520
Sir.

297
00:16:31,800 --> 00:16:33,120
Rumor has it

298
00:16:33,400 --> 00:16:34,440
