300
00:16:37,520 --> 00:16:38,280
Ghost painting?

301
00:16:38,560 --> 00:16:39,160
Yes.

302
00:16:40,800 --> 00:16:42,040
Let me tell you, Miss Lu.

303
00:16:42,960 --> 00:16:44,760
There was a famous serial murder
in Daling,

304
00:16:45,240 --> 00:16:46,240
and they were all related to a painting.

305
00:16:47,680 --> 00:16:48,280
Rumor has it

306
00:16:48,400 --> 00:16:49,360
that anyone who gets this painting

307
00:16:49,800 --> 00:16:51,080
will be burned alive.

308
00:16:51,360 --> 00:16:52,760
No one has been able
to break it for over ten years.

309
00:16:53,240 --> 00:16:54,200
Rumor says

310
00:16:54,840 --> 00:16:56,040
it was the ghost in the painting
that killed them.

311
00:16:57,520 --> 00:16:58,640
If my assumption is correct,

312
00:16:59,800 --> 00:17:00,720
Mr. Qian's death is also related

313
00:17:02,040 --> 00:17:03,080
to this painting.

314
00:17:05,480 --> 00:17:06,320
I didn't expect

315
00:17:06,960 --> 00:17:08,880
this case to show up in the capital now.

316
00:17:10,760 --> 00:17:11,320
Adviser.

317
00:17:12,320 --> 00:17:13,720
Go find the person in charge
of the house.

318
00:17:13,880 --> 00:17:14,360
Okay.

